name: Nft dashboard dark mode
description:
This is a free well designed nft dashboard dark mode. You can use it as you wish, feel free to add what you want.

What you will get

  • icons
  • glassmorphism cards
  • margins and paddings following the best conventions
  • 12 column layout grid
  • Components neatly grouped together etc

For collaboration you can email me at nanzingj@gmail.com
